shanthi &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; is a 1960 telugu drama film , produced by &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; nahatha , t. &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; under sri productions banner and directed by c. s. rao . starring akkineni nageswara rao , rajasulochana , kantha rao , krishna kumari , devika in lead roles and music composed by ghantasala . the film was remade in hindi as gharana ( 1961 film ) and much later remade as hindi movie ghar ghar ki kahani ( 1988 ) . it was dubbed into malayalam as shanthi nivas ( 1962 ) .